                <p>1. A substantial part of our increase in defense expenditures over the past four
                    years has gone into the increase in the number and strength of Army combat ready
                    divisions and Air Force tactical fighter wings. The latter are now being
                    equipped with F–4s and in <gloss target="#t_FY1">FY</gloss> 1966 we will make
                    our first large procurement of the F–111 (TFX).</p>
